      "message": "These half4(1)\u0027s are necessary here. Even though the children being sampled are always texture effects, all of these samples happen inside helper functions, so fInputColor (\"_input\") isn\u0027t visible. It seemed easier to just force the input color to white than to plumb the parent\u0027s input color in, knowing that it would be ignored.",
